{
  "stem": "9725.1",
  "chunk_idx": 4,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 8.1,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And she-- as a matter of fact, my other grandmother lived with us for-- for a while, too.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "So I was fortunate to have two grandmothers living with us.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And, you know, in retrospect, I wonder, when people today talk about, you know, families have to separate, there was just no-- at least, you know, I think when I look back, it seems almost too ideal.",
      "word_count": 37
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "And I wonder if it truly was as ideal, or if perhaps, that I have shut out in my memory things that might not have been.",
      "word_count": 26
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "But it has served me well during some very difficult times.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "And I see no reason why-- why I should not keep those memories.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "There was a great age difference between my two grandmothers.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "My paternal grandmother could have been my other grandmother's mother, almost.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "So there was no discrepancy in age.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "But I thought of it this morning-- I think one of the most tender memories that I have, was, you know, in the morning.",
      "word_count": 24
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "It was custom to get tea and milk in bed.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "And I remember my father carrying a tray for his mother, and my mother for her mother.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 15,
      "text": "And at times they would switch-- and-- with the others.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 16,
      "text": "And I think it was a beautiful thing.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 17,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] And I think I was very fortunate to have experienced that with my-- with my grandmothers.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 18,
      "text": "Where, unfortunately, my children never knew their grandparents.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 19,
      "text": "And I think that's a terrible void.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 20,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 5 SECONDS]",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 26,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "I attended elementary school at first.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 26,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And then I went to Catholic school.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 26,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "I went to a convent school called Notre Dame.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 26,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "It was taught by the sisters, by Franciscan sisters.",
      "word_count": 9
    }
  ],
